    <h1>Abel and Cain: The First Election</h1>
            <p class="page-subtitle">The Bible's First Story After the Fall Reveals God's Sovereign Distinction</p>
            <div class="page-meta">
                <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-icon">📖</span> Reading Time: ~15 min</div>
                <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-icon">⚡</span> Genesis 4:1–16, Hebrews 11:4</div>
                <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-icon">✦</span> Truth: Unconditional Election</div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <nav class="section-nav">
